in the 17th platoon, Layfon.

148
00:09:09,840 --> 00:09:10,680
Brother?

149
00:09:10,680 --> 00:09:12,880
What do you mean by
deception, anyway?

150
00:09:12,880 --> 00:09:13,720
Huh?

