00:21:29,280 --> 00:21:30,760
[MUSIC PLAYING]

433
00:21:30,760 --> 00:21:31,760
[EXPLOSION]

434
00:21:36,240 --> 00:21:37,680
External Ballistic Kei!

435
00:21:40,680 --> 00:21:41,640
Dragon Spiral Kei.

436
00:21:44,520 --> 00:21:45,320
Huh?

437
00:21:45,320 --> 00:21:46,160
Ah!

438
00:21:48,800 --> 00:21:50,760
Internal Augmented Spiral Kei.

439
00:21:54,240 --> 00:21:55,920
Was that Layfon?

440
00:21:55,920 --> 00:21:56,720
Yeah.

441
00:21:56,720 --> 00:21:57,920
It sure was.

