443
00:22:16,280 --> 00:22:19,000
[CHEERING]

444
00:22:19,000 --> 00:22:20,280
Yay!
All right!

445
00:22:20,280 --> 00:22:21,280
Layfie did it!

446
00:22:39,120 --> 00:22:42,080
You were incredible!

447
00:22:42,080 --> 00:22:43,560
You won't think that
when you see this.

448
00:22:43,560 --> 00:22:44,360
Huh?

449
00:22:44,360 --> 00:22:46,480
I'm really sorry, but
somehow, I burned out my DITE.

450
00:22:46,480 --> 00:22:48,160
I've never seen
